 《遣散》演员在纽约中央车站为粉丝表演真实场景https://www.nme.com/news/tv/severance-cast-act-out-real-scenes-in-new-yorks-grand-central-station-for-fans-3829290?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=遣散演员在纽约中央车站为粉丝表演真实场景Emma WilkesWed, 15 Jan 2025 19:58:42 +0000 NewsTV News https://www.nme.com/?p=3829290 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Severance_Photo_020104.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="亚当·斯科特在《遣散令》第二季中饰演马克·S。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Severance_Photo_020104.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Severance_Photo_020104-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Severance_Photo_020104-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Severance_Photo_020104-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Severance_Photo_020104-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Severance_Photo_020104-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>该剧第二季将于周五（1 月 17 日）开始</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/severance-cast-act-out-real-scenes-in-new-yorks-grand-central-station-for-fans-3829290">《Severance》后的演员们在纽约中央车站为粉丝们表演了真实的场景，</a>这首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Severance_Photo_020104.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="亚当·斯科特在《遣散令》第二季中饰演马克·S。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Severance_Photo_020104.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Severance_Photo_020104-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Severance_Photo_020104-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Severance_Photo_020104-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Severance_Photo_020104-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Severance_Photo_020104-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在第二季首播之前， <a href="https://www.nme.com/series/severance"><em>《Severance》</em></a>的演员们出现在纽约中央车站，扮演剧中的角色。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/tv-reviews/severance-season-2-review-mind-bending-sci-fi-apple-tv-3826803">《遣散费》第二季评论：令人费解的职场科幻小说</a></strong></li></ul><p>亚当·斯科特 (Adam Scott)、布里特·洛尔 (Britt Lower)、扎克·切里 (Zach Cherry) 和帕特里夏·阿奎特 (Patricia Arquette) 都扮演虚构生物技术公司 Lumon Industries 的员工，他们在一个复制 Lumon 宏观数据细化部门办公室的巨大玻璃盒子里进行表演。</p><p>人们看到演员们清理办公室地毯，在电脑上完成神秘的数据整理任务，并互相即兴对话，这让路过的粉丝们非常高兴。</p><p>该剧的导演兼制片人本·斯蒂勒在他的社交媒体账户上分享了一些宣传噱头的图片。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">现在是大中央。 <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Severance?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#Severance</a> <a href="https://t.co/VBcFzi4Bh3">pic.twitter.com/VBcFzi4Bh3</a></p><p> — 本·斯蒂勒 (@BenStiller) <a href="https://twitter.com/BenStiller/status/1879299981909323910?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2025 年 1 月 14 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>热门<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/apple-tv">Apple TV+</a>节目第二季将于本周五（1 月 17 日）首播。前两集将于当天播出，其余 8 集每周播出，直到 3 月 21 日大结局为止。据报道，每集的制作<a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-07-21/apple-tries-to-rein-in-hollywood-spending-after-years-of-losses">成本为苹果 2000 万美元</a>。</p><p> <em>《NME》</em>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/tv-reviews/severance-season-2-review-mind-bending-sci-fi-apple-tv-3826803">对第二季的五星级评论</a>中写道：“随着事情变得越来越有趣， <em>《遣散会》</em>是一部最好在高度警惕的情况下观看的节目。例如，背景中的涂鸦写着“谁还活着？”当<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-stone-roses">The Stone Roses</a>的《Love Spreads》配乐响起时，伊恩·布朗 (Ian Brown) 哀嚎着<em>“让我把你放进照片里/让我告诉你我的意思”，</em>你会祈求<em>Severance</em>团队也这么做。不过，不要强调它。享受这段旅程，让这个独特的表演挑逗和刺激你的大脑，直到你最终屈服。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/severance-cast-act-out-real-scenes-in-new-yorks-grand-central-station-for-fans-3829290">《Severance》后的演员们在纽约中央车站为粉丝们表演了真实的场景，</a>这首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
